Package com.sc2002.model

Class BTOProjectModel

java.lang.Object
com.sc2002.model.BTOProjectModel
public class BTOProjectModel extends Object
Represents a BTO (Build-To-Order) project with details such as project name, neighborhood, flat counts, application dates, and managing officers.

      public BTOProjectModel(String projectName, Neighborhood neighborhood, int twoRoomCount, int twoRoomPrice, int threeRoomCount, int threeRoomPrice, LocalDate openingDate, LocalDate closingDate, int maxManagingOfficer, int managerUserID)
      Constructs a new BTOProjectModel with the specified details. Assigns a unique project ID automatically.
      Parameters:
      projectName - The name of the project.
      neighborhood - The neighborhood where the project is located.
      twoRoomCount - The number of 2-room flats available.

      threeRoomCount - The number of 3-room flats available.
      threeRoomPrice - The price for 1 3-room flat.
      openingDate - The application opening date.
      closingDate - The application closing date.
      maxManagingOfficer - The maximum number of managing officers allowed.
      managerUserID - The User ID of the manager assigned to this project.
